The paper focuses on improving how machines can answer questions directly from text, which is a common topic in natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning. The use of recurrent networks and deep co-encoding also suggests a focus on neural network models, which are commonly used in NLP and related fields. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
